Invocation Name: tech helper
des:
If technical issues have happen to you before, they will happen again. When these devices stop working it can cause unnecessary stress. Now have your own personal assistant when your tech misbehaves.

Current supported issues:
-TV picture issues
-TV sound issues
-Streaming issues
-More to come...

This skill is for educational and informational purposes only and is made as a self-help tool for your own use.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
